Package: riskyr
Type: Package
Title: A Toolbox for Rendering Risk Literacy more Transparent 
Version: 0.1.0 
Date: 2018-02-16
Authors@R: c(person("Hansjoerg", "Neth", role = c("aut", "cre"),
